<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 24 Feb 2026 12:33:33 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>据称，总部位于香港的稳定币支付公司 RedotPay 考虑在美国进行 10 亿美元的 IPO</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-24/hk-based-stablecoin-payments-firm-redotpay-is-said-to-consider-1-billion-us-ipo</link><description>据知情人士透露，总部位于香港的稳定币支付公司 RedotPay 正在考虑在美国进行首次公开​​募股，可能筹集超过 10 亿美元的资金。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iKF5JN79A6fc/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Feb 2026 06:19:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-24/hk-based-stablecoin-payments-firm-redotpay-is-said-to-consider-1-billion-us-ipo</guid></item><item><title>Crypto.com 表示其获得了美国银行执照的有条件批准</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-23/crypto-com-says-it-won-conditional-approval-for-us-bank-charter</link><description>Crypto.com 表示，它获得了美国国家信托银行执照的有条件批准，为数字资产交易所作为联邦监管机构提供加密服务铺平了道路。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iNMaZUKmmfxw/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Feb 2026 19:27:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-23/crypto-com-says-it-won-conditional-approval-for-us-bank-charter</guid></item><item><title>比特币恢复下滑，风险较高的资产失宠</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-23/bitcoin-btc-slides-to-65-000-in-latest-bout-of-tariff-uncertainty</link><description>由于对企业利润的新一轮担忧，加上美国关税挥之不去的不确定性，压制了全球市场的风险偏好，比特币交易价格接近近期交易区间的下限。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iUL.YM6dAtRE/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Feb 2026 01:55:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-23/bitcoin-btc-slides-to-65-000-in-latest-bout-of-tariff-uncertainty</guid></item><item><title>特朗普家族的加密货币企业表示面临“协同攻击”</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-23/trump-family-s-crypto-venture-says-it-faced-coordinated-attack</link><description>由特朗普家族支持的数字资产企业世界自由金融公司表示，它击败了针对其旗舰加密货币产品的未具体说明的“协同攻击”。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iRXduF0GEhmw/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Feb 2026 17:07:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-23/trump-family-s-crypto-venture-says-it-faced-coordinated-attack</guid></item><item><title>塞勒的策略再次依靠普通股购买比特币，同时推销优先股</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-23/bitcoin-buyer-strategy-leans-on-common-stock-while-pitching-preferred-shares</link><description>Michael Saylor 的 Strategy Inc. 过去一周在比特币上花费了约 4000 万美元，完全通过出售普通股为加密货币累积器的最新购买提供资金，尽管该公司向投资者推销其永久优先股。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i3KwS_ksASuw/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Feb 2026 15:03:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-23/bitcoin-buyer-strategy-leans-on-common-stock-while-pitching-preferred-shares</guid></item><item><title>币安的赵在特朗普家族加密货币盛会上吹捧美国的增长目标</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-23/binance-s-zhao-touts-us-growth-bid-at-trump-family-crypto-bash</link><description>在获得总统赦免几个月后，币安联合创始人赵长鹏上周出现在海湖庄园，将自己完全置于特朗普家族的加密货币轨道上。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iBBQhy.GWp0c/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Feb 2026 13:47:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-23/binance-s-zhao-touts-us-growth-bid-at-trump-family-crypto-bash</guid></item><item><title>韩国央行敦促限制稳定币发行人的洗钱风险</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-23/bok-urges-limiting-stablecoin-issuers-on-money-laundering-risks</link><description>韩国央行重申其立场，即监管机构最初应仅授权获得许可的商业银行发行以韩元计价的稳定币，理由是担心洗钱和金融稳定风险。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iCoWwhk3TlWg/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Feb 2026 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-23/bok-urges-limiting-stablecoin-issuers-on-money-laundering-risks</guid></item><item><title>文克莱沃斯的双子座在加密货币崩溃后面临着硬着陆的风险</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-22/winklevoss-gemini-gemini-gemi-risks-a-hard-landing-after-crypto-rout</link><description>卡梅伦·文克莱沃斯 (Cameron Winklevoss) 和泰勒·文克莱沃斯 (Tyler Winklevoss) 花了十多年的时间，将 Gemini Space Station Inc. 打造成加密货币领域运行时间最长的交易所之一，也是首批获得美国主要监管机构批准的交易所之一，也是该行业丑闻和崩溃反复循环的幸存者。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i2C0YHjAaGpE/v2/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Feb 2026 14:30:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-22/winklevoss-gemini-gemini-gemi-risks-a-hard-landing-after-crypto-rout</guid></item></channel></rss>